{
  "stem": "1965.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now it is only because of power and greed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The greed to be in control, the greed to take the empowerment of someone else, bestow it on yourself, and have the total control of what you feel belongs to you and nobody else.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the same way here with the Nazi war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When I sat in a train in 1969 going from Muenchen to Hamburg, which is a good, nine-hour train ride, I sat with a German lady in a compartment talking for all these hours.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she told me, a single woman, that when she goes outside of Germany and a young man comes over to her to want to date her, and they find out she's from German ancestry and from Germany, they don't want to date her.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she asked me, why don't they want to date me?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no part in that war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told her the reason is because normally, wars is between soldiers on foot or in the air.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But never, when you take women, children, old people, and exterminate them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it's not war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Its genocide.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And genocide nobody forgets, and they can never forgive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I says, what Hitler did in the name of the Reich to implement that the Jews were making all the money, et cetera, and that the Germans were kept-- I says, you all were kept in a very, very weak position, because you all believed him.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what is the bottom line?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Germany will never be the same again because Germany will always suffer the persecution of one man, who gave orders to many others.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is your history.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is why people never forget, because that history is all over the world.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
